[
  {
    "id": "02eabcff-9012-44a9-aead-8add1d2ff366",
    "slug": "romanian-date-night-vocabulary",
    "title": "50+ Frasi Romene per Cene Romantiche Indimenticabili",
    "links_added": 1,
    "content_html": "<p>Una serata romantica con il tuo partner romeno sarà ancora più speciale se parli la sua lingua!</p>\n<h2>Invitare a Uscire</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-phrase my-8 relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-100 to-pink-100 rounded-2xl p-8\">\n  <div class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 text-6xl opacity-20\">💕</div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-accent font-bold mb-2\">\n    Frase da Imparare\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-header mb-2\">Vrei să ieșim la o întâlnire?</p>\n  <p class=\"text-lg text-gray-600 mb-1\">Vuoi uscire per un appuntamento?</p>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-accent\">[ vrei se ie-SHIM la o in-tel-NI-re ]</p>\n  <p class=\"mt-4 text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-4\">\n    L'invito perfetto per proporre un appuntamento.\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Ești liberă diseară?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Sei libera stasera?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">yeshti li-BE-re di-SEA-re</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Iubito, ești liberă diseară? Vreau să te duc la <a href=\"/learn/it/ro/romanian-restaurant-vocabulary-dining-out/\">restaurant</a>.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Hai să mergem la...</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Andiamo a...</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">hai se MER-gem la</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Hai să mergem la un film romantic!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Te invit la cină</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Ti invito a cena</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">te in-VIT la CI-ne</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Te invit la cină într-un loc special.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Al Ristorante</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">O masă pentru doi, vă rog</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Un tavolo per due, per favore</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">o MA-se pen-tru doi ve rog</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Bună seara. O masă pentru doi, vă rog.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Meniul, vă rog</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Il menu, per favore</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">me-NI-ul ve rog</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Ne puteți aduce meniul, vă rog?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Ce îmi recomandați?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Cosa mi consiglia?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">ce imi re-co-man-DAȚI</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Ce îmi recomandați ca specialitate a casei?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"my-8 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl\">🇷🇴</span>\n    <h4 class=\"font-bold text-amber-800 font-header\">Galateria Romena</h4>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text-amber-900\">\n    <p>In Romania, l&#39;uomo tradizionalmente paga il conto al primo appuntamento. Aprire la porta e tirare fuori la sedia sono gesti apprezzati.</p>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Complimenti per la Serata</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Arăți superb în seara asta</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Sei stupenda stasera</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">a-RĂȚI su-PERB in SEA-ra AS-ta</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Wow, arăți superb în seara asta, dragă!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Îmi place rochia ta</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Mi piace il tuo vestito</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">imi PLA-ce RO-kia ta</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Îmi place foarte mult rochia ta!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Ești cea mai frumoasă</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Sei la più bella</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">yeshti cea mai fru-MOA-să</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Pentru mine, ești cea mai frumoasă femeie.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Durante la Serata</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Romeno</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>Este delicios!</td>\n<td>È delizioso!</td>\n<td>ES-te de-li-CI-os</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Îmi place aici</td>\n<td>Mi piace qui</td>\n<td>imi PLA-ce a-ICI</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Ce seară minunată</td>\n<td>Che serata meravigliosa</td>\n<td>ce SEA-re mi-nu-NA-te</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Sunt fericit cu tine</td>\n<td>Sono felice con te</td>\n<td>sunt fe-ri-CIT cu TI-ne</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Să bem pentru noi!</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Brindiamo a noi!</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">se bem pen-tru noi</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Să bem pentru noi și pentru dragostea noastră!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Fine Serata</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">A fost o seară minunată</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">È stata una serata meravigliosa</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">a fost o SEA-ră mi-nu-NA-tă</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Mulțumesc, a fost o seară minunată cu tine.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Te mai pot vedea?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Posso rivederti?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">te mai pot ve-DEA</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Te mai pot vedea curând?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Te conduc acasă</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Ti accompagno a casa</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">te con-DUC a-CA-să</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Lasă-mă să te conduc acasă.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Vocabolario della Serata</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Romeno</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>întâlnire</td>\n<td>appuntamento</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>cinema</td>\n<td>cinema</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>restaurant</td>\n<td>ristorante</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>dans</td>\n<td>ballo</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>plimbare</td>\n<td>passeggiata</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>surpriză</td>\n<td>sorpresa</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>cadou</td>\n<td>regalo</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>lumânare</td>\n<td>candela</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>muzică</td>\n<td>musica</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>romantic</td>\n<td>romantico</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<div class=\"my-8 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl\">🇷🇴</span>\n    <h4 class=\"font-bold text-amber-800 font-header\">Luoghi Romantici</h4>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text-amber-900\">\n    <p>La Romania ha luoghi romantici incredibili: i caffè di Bucarest, i castelli della Transilvania, le spiagge del Mar Nero. Una serata in un &quot;birt&quot; (taverna tradizionale) è molto apprezzata!</p>\n\n  </div>\n</div>"
  },
  {
    "id": "2b483491-1cee-46ac-b1b5-6cc75b4ee4e3",
    "slug": "romanian-essential-phrases-for-couples",
    "title": "Romeno per Coppie: 40+ Frasi Essenziali",
    "links_added": 1,
    "content_html": "<p>Comunicare con il tuo partner romeno richiede alcune frasi fondamentali. Il romeno, come lingua romanza, ha molte similitudini con l&#39;italiano!</p>\n<h2>Frasi d&#39;Amore Quotidiane</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-phrase my-8 relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-100 to-pink-100 rounded-2xl p-8\">\n  <div class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 text-6xl opacity-20\">💕</div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-accent font-bold mb-2\">\n    Frase da Imparare\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-header mb-2\">Te iubesc foarte mult</p>\n  <p class=\"text-lg text-gray-600 mb-1\">Ti amo tantissimo</p>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-accent\">[ te iu-BESC FOAR-te mult ]</p>\n  <p class=\"mt-4 text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-4\">\n    L'espressione più intensa per dichiarare il tuo amore.\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Îmi lipsești</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Mi manchi</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">imi lip-SESHTI</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Îmi lipsești foarte mult când nu ești aici.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Ești totul pentru mine</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Sei tutto per me</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">yeshti TO-tul pen-tru MI-ne</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Iubito, ești totul pentru mine.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Nu pot trăi fără tine</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Non posso vivere senza di te</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">nu pot truh-EE FUH-ruh TI-ne</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Te iubesc, nu pot trăi fără tine.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Comunicazione Quotidiana</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Ce mai faci?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Come stai?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">che mai FACH</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Bună dragă, ce mai faci?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Cum a fost ziua ta?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Com'è stata la tua giornata?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">coom a fost ZEE-oo-a ta</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Bine ai venit acasă! Cum a fost ziua ta?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Te aștept acasă</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Ti aspetto a casa</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">te ash-TEPT a-CAH-suh</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Vino repede, te aștept acasă.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"my-8 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl\">🇷🇴</span>\n    <h4 class=\"font-bold text-amber-800 font-header\">Affetto Romeno</h4>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text-amber-900\">\n    <p>I romeni sono molto affettuosi in famiglia. Usano frequentemente diminutivi come &quot;dragă&quot; (caro), &quot;iubito&quot; (amore), &quot;puiule&quot; (piccolo mio).</p>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Fare Piani Insieme</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Vrei să ieșim diseară?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Vuoi uscire stasera?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">vrei se ie-SHIM di-SEA-re</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Dragă, vrei să ieșim diseară la <a href=\"/learn/it/ro/romanian-restaurant-vocabulary-dining-out/\">restaurant</a>?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Ce vrei să faci în weekend?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Cosa vuoi fare nel weekend?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">che vrey suh FACH een WII-kend</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Ce vrei să faci în weekend? Mergem la munte?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Hai să</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Andiamo a...</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">HAI suh</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Hai să mergem la cinema!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Esprimere Supporto</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Sunt aici pentru tine</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Sono qui per te</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">sunt a-ICI pen-tru TI-ne</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Orice s-ar întâmpla, sunt aici pentru tine.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Totul va fi bine</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Andrà tutto bene</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">TO-tul va fi BI-ne</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Nu te îngrijora, totul va fi bine.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Sunt mândru de tine</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Sono fiero/a di te</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">sunt MEN-dru de TI-ne</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Ai reușit! Sunt mândru de tine!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Tabella Rapida</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Romeno</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>Ti amo</td>\n<td>Te iubesc</td>\n<td>te iu-BESC</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Mi manchi</td>\n<td>Îmi lipsești</td>\n<td>imi lip-SESHTI</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Buonanotte</td>\n<td>Noapte bună</td>\n<td>NOAP-te BU-ne</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Ti voglio bene</td>\n<td>Te iubesc</td>\n<td>te iu-BESC</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Grazie amore</td>\n<td>Mulțumesc, dragă</td>\n<td>mul-zu-MESC DRA-ge</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Scusa</td>\n<td>Îmi pare rău</td>\n<td>imi PA-re reu</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Per favore</td>\n<td>Te rog</td>\n<td>te rog</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Sì, certo</td>\n<td>Da, sigur</td>\n<td>da si-GUR</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<div class=\"my-8 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl\">🇷🇴</span>\n    <h4 class=\"font-bold text-amber-800 font-header\">Lingua Romanza</h4>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text-amber-900\">\n    <p>Il romeno è l&#39;unica lingua romanza dell&#39;Europa orientale. Come italiano, deriva dal latino volgare, quindi troverai molte parole simili!</p>\n\n  </div>\n</div>"
  },
  {
    "id": "b3311dcc-9314-485e-8a3a-c4ed3a709515",
    "slug": "romanian-small-talk-conversation-starters",
    "title": "Conversazione in Rumeno: Frasi per Rompere il Ghiaccio",
    "links_added": 1,
    "content_html": "<p>Le grandi conversazioni spesso iniziano con piccole chiacchiere. Padroneggiare l&#39;arte dello small talk in rumeno ti permetterà di connetterti naturalmente con il tuo partner e la sua cerchia sociale.</p>\n<div class=\"speakable-phrase my-8 relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-100 to-pink-100 rounded-2xl p-8\">\n  <div class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 text-6xl opacity-20\">💕</div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-accent font-bold mb-2\">\n    Frase da Imparare\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-header mb-2\">Cum a fost ziua ta?</p>\n  <p class=\"text-lg text-gray-600 mb-1\">Com'è andata la giornata?</p>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-accent\">[ KOOM a FOST ZI-ua TA? ]</p>\n  <p class=\"mt-4 text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-4\">\n    Una domanda perfetta per iniziare qualsiasi conversazione\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Iniziare una Conversazione</h2>\n<p>Frasi per rompere il ghiaccio.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Romanian</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>How are you?</td>\n<td>Come stai?</td>\n<td>hau ar yu</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>How was your day?</td>\n<td>Com&#39;è andata la giornata?</td>\n<td>hau woz yor dei</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>What&#39;s new?</td>\n<td>Che c&#39;è di nuovo?</td>\n<td>wots niu</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>What are you up to?</td>\n<td>Cosa stai facendo?</td>\n<td>wot ar yu ap tu</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Ce mai faci?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Come stai?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">CHE mai FACH?</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Cum a fost ziua ta, dragă?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"my-8 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl\">🇷🇴</span>\n    <h4 class=\"font-bold text-amber-800 font-header\">Small Talk nella Cultura Rumeno</h4>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text-amber-900\">\n    <p>Lo small talk varia tra culture ma è un modo universale per connettersi.</p>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Domande sulla Giornata</h2>\n<p>Come chiedere e raccontare della propria giornata.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Romanian</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>How was work?</td>\n<td>Com&#39;è andato il lavoro?</td>\n<td>hau woz werk</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Tell me about your day</td>\n<td>Raccontami della tua giornata</td>\n<td>tel mi a-baut</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Anything interesting happen?</td>\n<td>È successo qualcosa?</td>\n<td>E-ni-thing IN-te-res-ting</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2>Weekend e Tempo Libero</h2>\n<p>Argomenti leggeri e piacevoli.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Romanian</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>Any plans for the weekend?</td>\n<td>Programmi per il weekend?</td>\n<td>E-ni plans</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>What do you want to do?</td>\n<td>Cosa vuoi fare?</td>\n<td>wot du yu wont</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Let&#39;s do something fun</td>\n<td>Facciamo qualcosa di divertente</td>\n<td>lets du SAM-thing</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2>Reazioni e Risposte</h2>\n<p>Come reagire durante la conversazione.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Romanian</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>That&#39;s interesting!</td>\n<td>Che interessante!</td>\n<td>dats IN-te-res-ting</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Really?</td>\n<td>Davvero?</td>\n<td>RI-li</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>That <a href=\"/learn/it/ro/romanian-pronunciation-guide-for-beginners/\">sounds</a> great</td>\n<td>Sembra fantastico</td>\n<td>dat saunds greit</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">E interesant!</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Che interessante!</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">E in-te-re-SANT!</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"E interesant!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Consigli per lo Small Talk</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Fai domande aperte</strong>: Evita risposte sì/no</li>\n<li><strong>Ascolta attivamente</strong>: Mostra interesse genuino</li>\n<li><strong>Condividi anche tu</strong>: È bidirezionale</li>\n<li><strong>Mantieni leggerezza</strong>: Evita argomenti pesanti</li>\n<li><strong>Pratica ogni giorno</strong>: Anche pochi minuti aiutano</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Per conversazioni più profonde, esplora le <a href=\"/romanian-expressing-emotions\">frasi per emozioni</a> e i <a href=\"/romanian-pet-names-terms-of-endearment\">vezzegiativi</a>.</p>"
